channel.title: Need help with tom's cache suite
channel.description: Every time i try to use tom's cache suite to open files it won't work. I click load cache, then i surf through my files and when i get to the folder with my cache in it, it shows the folder as empty. Yet it has all the cache when i open the folder up without using toms cache suite. Maybe i need to download a later version of it if possible?
